---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Tony Rosen">
	<main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-24 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
		<article class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-slate-100 dark:text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-400 mb-8">
				Last updated: December 17, 2025
			</p>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-slate-100 dark:text-white">Overview</h2>
				<p class="mb-4 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">
					This is a personal portfolio website. I collect minimal information to
					understand how visitors use the site and to improve the experience.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-slate-100 dark:text-white">Information Collection</h2>
				<p class="mb-4 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">This website uses analytics services to collect:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">
					<li>Pages you visit and time spent on the site</li>
					<li>Browser type, device, and operating system</li>
					<li>Referring website or source</li>
					<li>
						General location (city/country level) based on IP address, not
						precise geolocation
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-slate-100 dark:text-white">
					Third-Party Services & Cookies
				</h2>
				<p class="mb-4 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">This site uses the following analytics services:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">
					<li>
						<strong>Google Analytics</strong> - For website traffic analysis
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>PostHog</strong> - For product analytics and session
						recordings
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>LinkedIn Insights</strong> - For LinkedIn ad conversion
						tracking
					</li>
					<li><strong>RB2B</strong> - For B2B visitor identification</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mb-4 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">
					When you visit or log in to our website, cookies and similar
					technologies may be used by our online data partners or vendors to
					associate these activities with other personal information they or
					others have about you, including by association with your email. We
					(or service providers on our behalf) may then send communications and
					marketing to these email addresses. You may opt out of receiving this
					advertising by visiting <a
						href="https://app.retention.com/optout"
						class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer">https://app.retention.com/optout</a
					>.
				</p>
				<p class="mb-4 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">
					You also have the option to opt out of the collection of your personal
					data in compliance with GDPR. To exercise this option, please visit <a
						href="https://www.rb2b.com/rb2b-gdpr-opt-out"
						class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						>https://www.rb2b.com/rb2b-gdpr-opt-out</a
					>.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-slate-100 dark:text-white">How I Use Information</h2>
				<p class="mb-4 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">I use collected information to:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">
					<li>Understand which content is most valuable to visitors</li>
					<li>Improve website performance and user experience</li>
					<li>Identify technical issues</li>
					<li>
						Understand the professional audience visiting the site for potential
						business opportunities
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-slate-100 dark:text-white">Data Sharing</h2>
				<p class="mb-4 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">
					Your data is processed by the third-party analytics services mentioned
					above. I do not sell personal information. Each service has its own
					privacy policy governing how they handle data:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">
					<li>
						<a
							href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
							class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics Privacy Policy</a
						>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a
							href="https://posthog.com/privacy"
							class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer">PostHog Privacy Policy</a
						>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a
							href="https://www.linkedin.com/legal/privacy-policy"
							class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn Privacy Policy</a
						>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a
							href="https://www.rb2b.com/privacy-policy"
							class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer">RB2B Privacy Policy</a
						>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-slate-100 dark:text-white">Your Rights</h2>
				<p class="mb-4 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">You have the right to:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">
					<li>Opt out of analytics tracking using the links provided above</li>
					<li>Use browser settings to block cookies</li>
					<li>Use browser extensions or privacy tools to block trackers</li>
					<li>
						Request information about data collected (though this is a personal
						site with minimal data retention)
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-slate-100 dark:text-white">Contact</h2>
				<p class="mb-4 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">
					For questions about this privacy policy, please contact me through the
					contact information provided on this website.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-slate-100 dark:text-white">Changes to This Policy</h2>
				<p class="mb-4 text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-300">
					I may update this privacy policy occasionally. The "Last updated" date
					at the top will reflect when changes were made.
				</p>
			</section>
		</article>
	</main>
</Layout>
